      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          <% 5.times do %><%= lucide_icon "star", class: "w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current" %><% end %>
        </div>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">"一个人，靠大胜龙虾，我做到了以前三人团队才能交付的事情。AI 时代，一人公司真的可以很强。"</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=40&h=40&fit=crop&crop=face" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" alt="用户">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">李总</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted">独立创业者</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          <% 5.times do %><%= lucide_icon "star", class: "w-4 h-4 text-secondary fill-current" %><% end %>
        </div>
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">"Cursor 解决的是写代码的问题，大胜龙虾解决的是整个研发团队怎么跟 AI 协同的问题，层次完全不一样。"</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?w=40&h=40&fit=crop&crop=face" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" alt="用户">
